reviews.review_text:
nice show this is a great show although second set a lot better than the first IMO. finally that dude shouting all along the watchtower can shut up, he's screaming it since the first song.

anyway, good crazy fingers, exceptional PITB and great show all around....funny stage banter in the first set...we want 'steve'!
